                            <additions>
                                <p>
                                    <locus from="2" to="165" scheme="folios"/>
                                    <note>Scattered throughout the manuscript are numbers written in pencil by a modern hand (most likely by the bookbinder), e.g. <locus from="57r" to="57r" scheme="folios"/> bottom left corner. It is unclear what they refer to.</note>
                                </p>
